== Documentation ==
This template is used to denote when a page is not officially endorsed by VRChat and will automatically add the "Community Page" category.

=== Example Usage ===
<code><nowiki>{{Noticebox/Community}}</nowiki></code>

will make:
{{Noticebox/Community}}

It has no extra parameters.

